  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Intelligent Qube is a puzzle game for the PlayStation. In the game, the player controls a character who must run around a platform made of cubes, clearing certain cubes as they approach. Cubes are \"cleared\" by marking a spot on the stage, waiting for the cube to roll on top of it, and then deactivating the marked spot.",
